DS-0013 (MEDIUM): RUN should not be used to change directory: 'cd /tmp &&     git clone --branch PG17/v1.6.0-rc0 https://github.com/apache/age.git &&     cd age &&     make PG_CONFIG=/usr/lib/postgresql/17/bin/pg_config install ||     (echo "Failed to build AGE" && exit 1)'. Use 'WORKDIR' statement instead.
════════════════════════════════════════
Use WORKDIR instead of proliferating instructions like 'RUN cd … && do-something', which are hard to read, troubleshoot, and maintain.

See https://avd.aquasec.com/misconfig/ds-0013
